Where:

- application - `scene_server` main program
- InterfaceSup - `Interface` module supervisor process
- AoiSup - `AOI` management module supervisor process
- PlayerManagerSup - player management `PlayerManager` module supervisor process
- PlayerCharacterSup - player process `PlayerCharacter` module supervisor process
- Aoi - `AOI` management module process
- PlayerManager - player management module process
- PlayerCharacter - player process

